      <section>
         <title>Chrome</title>
            <p>Sorry - no support. Chrome uses Google's own spelling checker,
            which we don't have access to. And Google does not support the
            languages we are working on (please prove us wrong, Google!).</p>
      </section>

      <section>
         <title>Safari</title>
            <p>Safari uses the OS-wide spelling service in OSX. See the download
            options on the page for <a href="oswide.html">OS-wide spelling checkers</a>.</p>
      </section>

